Package com.itkolleg.bookingsystem.repos.timeslot

Interface TimeslotRepo

All Known Implementing Classes:
TimeslotRepo_JPAH2
public interface TimeslotRepo
interface for handling operations related to time slots. Includes methods to add, retrieve, update, and delete time slots.

2023-05-24
